    <title>About this Manual</title>
    <note>
        <para>This manual is about using <productname>DocBridge Pilot</productname> through the Web Interface.</para>
    </note>
    <sect1 label=" ">
        <title>Target Audience</title>
        <para>This manual is written for guidance and instruction of those who are responsible for the operation and administration of <productname>DocBridge Pilot</productname>.</para>
    </sect1>
    <sect1 label=" ">
        <title>Structure of the Manual</title>
        <para><xref linkend="pilot_architecture_intro"/> describes the product structure of <productname>&dbpi;</productname> and explains basic concepts.</para>
        <para><xref linkend="db_pil_wui_generaluseractions"/> provides an introduction into general user actions in the Web Interface such as logging into the system or changing the application language.</para>
        <para><xref linkend="db_pil_browser_webinterface"/> provides a general overview of <productname>&dbpi;</productname> Web Interface.</para>
    </sect1>

